<paragraph blockId="66.[189,1398,955,1017]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
Very rare, only known from a couple of specimens from sand dunes in Southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1177,1274,955,981]" name="Sweden" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Sweden</collectingCountry>
. Only one recent record from Koster, an island on the West coast of 
<collectingCountry box="[863,960,990,1016]" name="Sweden" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Sweden</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
